Catch Fire by Ghostfacers

59
00:03:18,155 --> 00:03:19,530
Oi.

60
00:03:19,531 --> 00:03:21,056
Que diabos é isso?

61
00:03:21,239 --> 00:03:23,682
- Um croissookie.
- Um croissookie?

62
00:03:23,683 --> 00:03:25,168
Sim, são os novos cronuts.

63
